StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetProgramTypes]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
select program_type_code as ProgramTypeCode, program_type_descrip.on as ProgramTypeDescrip.on from mcriss.dbo.program_type FOR XML PATH('ProgramType'), ROOT('ProgramTypes')
